{"tid":2051667,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"親歷好友被消失 覺悟再無缺席理由  新移民首踏維園感受燭海","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T04:46:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a03d34ab3f41d67ab3680891ff638b112b58805f","tid":2051667,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/APMT3VBSBUGSB322F4B3WRRCII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2FAPMT3VBSBUGSB322F4B3WRRCII%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EtAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=210922f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2FAPMT3VBSBUGSB322F4B3WRRCII%2F&h=fb15dc28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/APMT3VBSBUGSB322F4B3WRRCII/</a><br />\n<br />\n親歷好友被消失 覺悟再無缺席理由 <br />\n新移民首踏維園感受燭海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J8JC0vF4t8DSAFXYsxdBRwILpVo=/802x531/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JKQ35NVJX5NDZKL2LVP6HTDJEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ8JC0vF4t8DSAFXYsxdBRwILpVo%3D%2F802x531%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJKQ35NVJX5NDZKL2LVP6HTDJEU.jpg&h=db044576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒有大台，沒有政府批准，大批港人昨晚堅持憑良心出席六四集會。許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府以限聚令為由禁制六四維園集會，國安法的恐懼又籠罩全城，但千難萬難，烙印在心的六四國殤又豈會因此而磨滅？這次「最後」集會，讓在港定居的方小姐首次來到維園出席悼念六四的燭光集會。在內地出生成長，經歷八九民運、好友被消失，使上半生遠離政治的她「再冇缺席理由」，獨一無二的燭海曾令她萬分感動，希望趕及在被消失前成為一分子。<br />\n<br />\n記者：呂麗嬋 梁穎童<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fImtPi1zAp97v0kdkIfPZoLW9YU=/802x1074/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U7ANIZU7QQAA7F442WWZD2ODFE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfImtPi1zAp97v0kdkIfPZoLW9YU%3D%2F802x1074%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU7ANIZU7QQAA7F442WWZD2ODFE.gif&h=026b25ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地出生的方小姐有感生活離不開政治，昨終踏進維園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y8RZin9WP3ftBxgzUhuwGAeYXhQ=/802x1074/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QYNPTJUMVYM6TWJNWT247GLTYA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy8RZin9WP3ftBxgzUhuwGAeYXhQ%3D%2F802x1074%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQYNPTJUMVYM6TWJNWT247GLTYA.gif&h=ec18e124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿鋒指無論是否自認中國人，都應悼念六四犧牲青年。<br />\n<br />\n在內地出生、自言政治冷感的方小姐，。。。。。。。。。。。。，「向來對政治唔敏感，直至有個朋友（數年前）喺北京飛嚟香港，突然唔見咗，我先真正覺得原來可以咁近，可以咁得人驚」。<br />\n<br />\n1989年學運席捲全國，在深圳讀大學的她記得校園貼滿大字報，。。。。。。。。。。。。。」。<br />\n<br />\n林氏夫婦堅持悼念六四，彌補以前不敢做的事情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反送中啟蒙青年了解歷史<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警屯重兵動口不動手  為惡法製和平假象<br />\n<br />\n除了方小姐，趕尾班車見證維園燭光的，還有阿鋒。穿着白T恤、獨自坐在維園一角低頭看手機直播的他，自言今次是第一次出席維園六四集會。過往不太了解政治，他自言對六四一無所知，但去年的反送中運動成了他的政治啟蒙。阿鋒認為出席六四集會只與良知攸關，「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無論認同自己係中國人與否，都應該一齊懷緬嗰啲幾十年前犧牲嘅勇敢青年</strong></span></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n不理限聚令來到維園的，還有回流的K叔（化名）。早年移民澳洲、。。。。。。。。。。，即使危險也無阻他出席六四集會的決心。<br />\n<br />\n「無論將來有。。。。。。。。。。和理非眼中的勇武，勇武眼中的和理非：「其實係乜都好，都係政府逼出嚟。」預早來維園「睇位」，研究定「逃亡路線」，做過懲教署的他直言擔心悼念變衝突，殺錯良民，幸好他對「走。。。。。。。住佢走。」像這樣打遊擊式悼念六四，林說還是首次：「冇辦法，𠵱家嗰政府係咁。」"},{"pid":"ff326dfad93fda9e5abc44e535e28e812895205f","tid":2051667,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J8JC0vF4t8DSAFXYsxdBRwILpVo=/802x531/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JKQ35NVJX5NDZKL2LVP6HTDJEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ8JC0vF4t8DSAFXYsxdBRwILpVo%3D%2F802x531%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJKQ35NVJX5NDZKL2LVP6HTDJEU.jpg&h=db044576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒有大台，沒有政府批准，大批港人昨晚堅持憑良心出席六四集會。許頌明攝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6192feac430e7c225d400649ce63d8b3472a020c","tid":2051667,"uid":359419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:32:02.000Z","msg":"不過入錢入錢果到其實睇到好撚傷心...."},{"pid":"f5a130df6607eb836f3e98a7d3069ac487573f96","tid":2051667,"uid":216441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}